3.00	Gregor_Robertson_(footballer)	Gregor Robertson (footballer)	Gregor Aedan Robertson (born 19 January 1984 in Edinburgh) is a Scottish footballer who plays for Chesterfield. His favoured position is left-back but he can also play on the left side of midfield and more recently has enjoyed a successful spell at centre back.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8f/Gregor_robertson.jpg/200px-Gregor_robertson.jpg
